; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 1036-1037
; Tests the check directive inside auto transactions.
; When an auto transaction has a 'check' directive that evaluates to false,
; a warning is issued but processing continues.

= /Expenses:Food/
    check amount > 100
    (Budget:Food)              -1.0

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
             $-50.00  Budget:Food
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
             $-50.00
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 12: Transaction check failed: (amount > {100})
end test
